snippet.title: Mining Rail - Trailer Xbox
snippet.description:
Mining Rail is a roller coaster game.

Get into in your mine cart and drive at high speed along the railway track, getting through the mine to the exit and down to the valley. The track is steep, the curves tight and the force tries to take your vehicle out of the bend.
 
Find your way through the Ghost Mine and the most impressive mines around the world and start a journey from deep inside the mountains down to the safe station at the end of the track.
